Blue
====

Blue is a content management system foundation used to create adminable websites.


Install
=======

1. Add as a submodule
git submodule add git@github.com:bluespan/blue.git vendor/plugins/blue
git submodule init
git submodule update

2. Bootstrap
rake blue:bootstrap

3. Install gems
rake gems:install

4. Run Migrations
rake db:migrate

5. Create Admin
rake blue:create:admin

6. Remove default routes
map.connect ':controller/:action/:id'
map.connect ':controller/:action/:id.:format'

7. Launch server
script/server

